		, sourceCte(DateKey, ActualDate, DateNameEU, DateNameUS, EnglishMonthCode, EnglishMonthName, EnglishDayCode, EnglishDayName, YearMonth, YearQuarter, IsWeekend, IsLastDayInMonth
